This Chrome extension transforms your new tab with a unique perspective, featuring a cozy recreation room surrounded by the mesmerizing world of an aquarium. Watch as fish swim peacefully by, creating a tranquil and immersive atmosphere, perfect for relaxing and enjoying your browsing experience.

Features:
🐠 Beautiful live wallpaper of a recreation room inside a peaceful aquarium.
🌐 Customizable search bar to use your preferred search engine.
🕒 Clock and date display to keep you organized.
🔗 Quick-access shortcuts for easy navigation to your favorite websites.
Let the calming presence of underwater life and a cozy space enhance your browsing experience every time you open a new tab.
